1. Open the Doordash app 
2. Browse pizza places 
3. Decide on pizza place 
4. Check menu 
5. Decide on pizza flavor
6. Order the pizza 
7. Wait on order 
8. Tip the delivery person 
9. Enjoy the pizza  
9. a) If pizza is the wrong order, contact Doordash support 
10. Explain to Doordash representative the issue 
11. Listen to alternative solutions given by the representative 
12. Follow the solution that best fits your solution to the issue 